(158, 134, 'awareness', '1', 'Hepatitis A and what parents need to know', '<p>According to WHO report in developing countries, about 90% of children under 10 years old are infected with hepatitis A. Until now, there is no specific treatment for hepatitis A in the world. Food safety and hygiene, vaccination against hepatitis A are the most effective preventive measures.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#575757\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#575757\"><img alt=\"/\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/BiiGGFPxOklasmO1kzvPDWd1mAURQoTkj46GyEHReePBsIc71Lzj_c4_4yX3BWojhdVvABsruNqFTFRnAUSJ5O3c86wIr7Cq8jGobie6gF7jJMaZzIUvP3VfEYb7Y-B5tW-rr_k\" style=\"height:530px; width:531px\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#575757\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#575757\"><img alt=\"/\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/gB3xQim7XYYhBj4bvZbWaK-OV2AxkTNeM1hSacI87yaqoTTvyqm1znM0Ws_YWviK6VN70ilYLDwwZFAejoGSEX6myzBgTQbECgzMnvCZlmE0ER6VbpwjDFTuJ079Oe4mQvXkJFQ\" style=\"height:699px; width:700px\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#575757\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#575757\"><img alt=\"/\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/adehSOJRNX75LPzkmJ9rAgKpgXfypWmHWEdoMBh4U4-AmDICWD4uFqIvQD3OUd2cNcpldtwM70PqLGZxHs3WHvLKEhzKR192dLJELwe1DzoDXElc1mfHCYBZDqgxWZLbqMd3XFk\" style=\"height:699px; width:700px\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#575757\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#575757\"><img alt=\"/\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/oYwVyB0txDCrrK7vTy3k8g1OOc7zDHFIFg69XLF7wnPiAZjk_Cnt7iFc34pXdrgumULA4eu2w5B1OQZWudXRTgYATSDedQC0_ddqwuRHzAogZKAxutLP7hBQAHTcFUp2LZJxp6Q\" style=\"height:700px; width:700px\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#575757\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#575757\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'Viêm gan A và những điều ba mẹ c